    h1 About Me
    p Welcome to my blog! I'm Changyi Yang, a data scientist and software developer based in Carnegie Mellon University. Here, I share insights on software development, data science, and cutting-edge technology.
    
    h2 My Background
    p With a background in computer science and extensive experience in backend development, I've worked on various projects ranging from building a food delivery platform to optimizing machine learning models for business intelligence.
    
    h2 My Passion
    p My passion is in exploring how data-driven solutions can impact the world. This blog is a space for me to discuss new findings, share practical tips, and sometimes, just jot down interesting concepts I'm learning or working on.

